wdi2-SH.ANM.NPRG.ZS.def: Prevalence of anemia, non-pregnant women, is the percentage of non-pregnant women whose hemoglobin level is less than 120 grams per liter at sea level.
wdi2-SH.ANM.NPRG.ZS.name: Prevalence of anemia among non-pregnant women
wdi2-SH.ANM.NPRG.ZS.source: World Health Organization, Global Health Observatory Data Repository/World Health Statistics.
